name: Black Golden Nug Pocket Tee
description:
Printed on an extremely soft pocket tee. Our first shirt helps bring back simplicity to the streetwear world. This pocket tee was designed in the idea that thing's are not always what they seem.

+ Extremely Limited. 
+ We ship Worldwide. 
+ All sales are final.

* FOR BEST RESULTS: Machine wash cold separately, hang to dry. Do not bleach. Do not iron on the print. Do not dry-clean or use softeners.

*Please allow 2-4 business days to receive your order in the Canada after it has been shipped. All International customers please allow 7-10 business days to receive your order after it has been shipped
